# Copied from parameters for zinc.
NAME CD
IO_STRING  CD Z
TYPE LIGAND
PROPERTIES METAL
AA UNK
ROTAMERS BASIC
ATOM CD   Cd    CD      2.00
ATOM  V1  VIRT  VIRT    0.00
ATOM  V2  VIRT  VIRT    0.00
ATOM  V3  VIRT  VIRT    0.00
ATOM  V4  VIRT  VIRT    0.00
BOND CD    V1
BOND CD    V2
BOND CD    V3
BOND CD    V4
CHARGE CD FORMAL +2
NET_FORMAL_CHARGE +2
NBR_ATOM CD
NBR_RADIUS 5.0
